Package: pooling
Type: Package
Title: Fit Poolwise Regression Models
Version: 1.1.2
Date: 2020-02-12
Author: Dane R. Van Domelen
Maintainer: Dane R. Van Domelen <vandomed@gmail.com>
Description: Functions for calculating power and fitting regression
        models in studies where a biomarker is measured in "pooled"
        samples rather than for each individual. Approaches for
        handling measurement error follow the framework of Schisterman
        et al. (2010) <doi:10.1002/sim.3823>.
License: GPL-3
